extends layout

block content
    div(class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center min-h-screen bg-gray-100")
        div(class="w-full max-w-4xl bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8 text-center")
            img(src="https://mypicgogo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/tuchuang202402070012483.jpg" alt="Logo" class="mb-6 w-24 h-24 mx-auto rounded-full")
            h1(class="text-3xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-6")= title
            p(class="text-gray-600 mb-8") Welcome #{name}
            div(class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8")
                div
                    a(href="/movies" class="bg-green-500 hover:bg-green-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline block mb-4") Go to the movies
                div
                    a(href="/contacts" class="bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-2 px-6 rounded focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline block") Go to the contacts

            // Course Introduction
            div(class="text-left mt-12")
                h2(class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4") Course Introduction
                p(class="text-gray-600 mb-4") This course covers the fundamental concepts and techniques of full-stack web development, focusing on server-delivered front-end content such as server-rendered HTML or JSON and its integration with back-end architectures and data stores.

            // Acknowledgement
            div(class="text-left mt-12")
                h2(class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4") Acknowledgement
                p(class="text-gray-600 mb-4") A heartfelt thank you to Professor Brian Bailey for his invaluable guidance and support throughout this course. His expertise and dedication have been instrumental in my learning journey.

            // Contact Information
            div(class="text-left mt-12")
                h2(class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-4") Contact Information
                p(class="text-gray-600 mb-4") Email: meetyifan@gmail.com
                p(class="text-gray-600") GitHub Repository:
                    a(href="https://github.com/oreoft/ITMD542-S24.git" class="text-blue-500 hover:text-blue-600") https://github.com/oreoft/ITMD542-S24.git

